description: Prince Joachim, who contracted coronavirus after attending a party in Spain, "regrets" his actions.
title: Coronavirus: Belgian Prince Joachim apologises for Spanish lockdown party
title_page: Coronavirus: Belgian Prince Joachim apologises for Spanish lockdown party - BBC News
maintext: Spain is in the process of emerging from one of the strictest lockdowns in Europe. It outlined a four-stage plan on 4 May to start easing the lockdown, which saw children under the age of 14 confined to their homes for six weeks.
